GET http://localhost:3001

### Criar usuário
POST http://localhost:3001/users/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Rafael",
  "email": "rafa@email.com",
  "password": "1234567"
}

### Login de Usuário
POST http://localhost:3001/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "rafa@email.com",
    "password": "1234567"
}

